Package: evanverse
Type: Package
Title: Utility Functions for Data Analysis and Visualization
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Evan", "Zhou", email = "evanzhou.bio@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0009-4600-8175"))
Description: A collection of utility functions to support data analysis
    and visualization in R. The package provides helpers for string
    manipulation, file handling, color palettes, bioinformatics data
    conversion, and common plotting tasks.
